name: DROWNED V - DUNKELHEIT
description: Here I am at the end of our story, but there is something wrong even if everything seems right, like something left out to realize this ending, I know you're listening ARCHITECT, this is not the ending I seek, this is not the story I told you, I know you'll only just regress again to another world, but I'll find you, I'll be there I know your secret now.
